================================================================================================
= now depending of what ubuntu version you have, you have to get the right one for you on this = 
= step											       =
================================================================================================

Ubuntu 21.10 	sudo add-apt-repository 'deb https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/ impish main'
Ubuntu 21.04 	sudo add-apt-repository 'deb https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/ hirsute main'
Ubuntu 20.10 or Ubuntu 20.04	sudo add-apt-repository 'deb https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/ groovy main'

Linux Mint 20.x    sudo add-apt-repository 'deb https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/ focal main'

Ubuntu 18.04 or Linux Mint 19.x     sudo add-apt-repository 'deb https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/ bionic main' 

